      Minimum net load Δ Lmin of microgrid system and distributed energy storage system discharges threshold value Δ Pdis are set, Δ Pdis>Δ Lmin; It is the net load Δ Load of system that the overall load of user deducts the distributed generation system generate output;
      < when Δ Lmin and the current capacity of distributed energy-storage system did not reach its upper energy limit, energy-storage system charged, absorbing redundant active power as Δ Load;
      As Δ Load>Δ Pdis and the current capacity of distributed energy-storage system do not reach under its energy in limited time, and energy storage system discharges discharges active power and supplies with user load, and wherein system's net load deducts the energy storage delivered power unnecessary part is provided by public electric wire net.
